1. Installed nvm by running:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Exited and reopened the terminal.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16 by running:
   nvm install 20.16

4. Installed SASS globally by running:
   npm install -g sass

5. Verified installation with:
   sass --version
